            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...H-hello."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...D-do you need something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, no, sorry about that. I just didn't recognize you, where did you come from?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...I've always lived here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Huh? You have? You look very unique, I doubt I would forget you if I saw you before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I just normally don't come here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I live near the edge of town..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know... You're wearing unusual clothes, I've never seen anything like it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...Are they really unusual? I never noticed until now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Although the neighbors do say that a lot. But I like them, they're really open and breathable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, it looks really cool!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Anyway, I'll be leaving."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "...What was she doing? I didn't even get a chance to ask her name."
